long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Once authenticated with your GitHub account, we automate the entire process, syncing your submissions without any additional effort. No more tedious copy-pasting. Your GitHub repositories stay up-to-date with your latest LeetCode achievements in real-time. Say goodbye to the hassle of managing multiple platforms manually. Install SyncLeet today and let your GitHub profile truly reflect your coding prowess with the seamless synchronization it deserves!

What's New (August 14, 2024):
- Fetch Past Submission Histories: Sync your entire LeetCode history with GitHub.
- Push Notifications: Receive alerts when your submissions are successfully pushed to GitHub.
- GitHub Autolinks: Automatically link to the relevant problem on GitHub.

p.s. Built by two Carnegie Mellon students practing LeetCode for their job interviews.
